      {
        "@value": "Characteristic rhythm at 14-20 Hz, detected most prominently over the posterior regions of the head. May alternate or be intermixed with alpha rhythm. Blocked or attenuated by attention, especially visual, and mental effort."
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label": [
